{% comment %}
  Primavera Flowers, single self-contained homepage section.
  Renders everything (hero, promise band, Madres, occasions, products,
  photo promise, reviews, coverage, subs teaser, editorial) without
  depending on settings or blocks, so it cannot end up empty due to
  Theme Editor stored-state drift.
  Voice rules: no em dashes, simple, sharp.
{% endcomment %}

<style>
  .ph {
    --sage:#a8b59a; --sage-deep:#7a8a6f; --sage-soft:#c8d2bc;
    --cream:#f5efe2; --cream-2:#ece4d2; --paper:#faf6ec;
    --ink:#2a2620; --ink-2:#5a544c; --ink-3:#8a847c;
    --rose:#d39283; --rose-deep:#b8705d; --line:#e2dac7;
    --ph-serif:"DM Serif Display","Times New Roman",serif;
    --ph-sans:"Inter",system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream); color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--ph-sans);
    font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.55; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }
  .ph *, .ph *::before, .ph *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  .ph a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
  .ph img { display: block; max-width: 100%; }

  /* Hero */
  .ph-hero { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; min-height: 640px; }
  .ph-hero-text { padding: 72px 56px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
  .ph-eyebrow { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--sage-deep); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px; display: inline-block; }
  .ph-hero h1 { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 68px); line-height: 1.05; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 22px; max-width: 540px; }
  .ph-hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--sage-deep); }
  .ph-lede { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--ink-2); max-width: 480px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .ph-hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .ph-btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 14px 26px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; transition: all .15s; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; }
  .ph-btn-primary { background: var(--sage-deep); color: var(--cream); }
  .ph-btn-primary:hover { background: var(--ink); }
  .ph-btn-ghost { color: var(--sage-deep); border: 1.5px solid var(--sage-deep); padding: 12px 24px; background: transparent; }
  .ph-btn-ghost:hover { background: var(--sage); color: var(--cream); border-color: var(--sage); }
  .ph-review-line { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-2); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 24px; display: inline-block; }
  .ph-review-line .stars { color: #f5b454; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-right: 6px; }
  .ph-hero-meta { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); padding-top: 20px; gap: 20px; }
  .ph-hero-meta .ph-label { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-3); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .ph-hero-meta .ph-val { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-size: 22px; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.1; }
  .ph-hero-meta .ph-val small { font-family: var(--ph-sans); font-size: 12px; display: block; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: 4px; font-weight: 500; }
  .ph-hero-image { position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: var(--cream-2); }
  .ph-hero-image img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .ph-hero-tag { position: absolute; bottom: 24px; left: 24px; background: var(--cream); padding: 14px 18px; max-width: 240px; border-radius: 6px; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
  .ph-hero-tag .ph-tag-label { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--sage-deep); font-weight: 600; }
  .ph-hero-tag .ph-tag-name { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-size: 20px; color: var(--ink); margin-top: 4px; line-height: 1.2; }
  .ph-hero-tag .ph-tag-price { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: 4px; }

  /* Promise */
  .ph-promise { background: var(--sage-deep); color: var(--cream); padding: 56px 40px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 40px; }
  .ph-promise .ph-num { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; color: var(--sage-soft); font-weight: 600; }
  .ph-promise .ph-title { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.2; margin: 10px 0 8px; }
  .ph-promise .ph-desc { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.55; color: rgba(245,239,226,.85); }

  /* Madres */
  .ph-madres { background: var(--paper); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .ph-madres-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: stretch; }
  .ph-madres-text { padding: 72px 48px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
  .ph-ribbon { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rose-deep); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .ph-madres-text h2 { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(36px, 4.5vw, 60px); line-height: 1.05; color: var(--ink); }
  .ph-madres-text h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--sage-deep); }
  .ph-madres-text .ph-es { font-size: 18px; color: var(--ink-2); margin-top: 18px; max-width: 460px; line-height: 1.55; }
  .ph-madres-text .ph-en { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--ink-2); max-width: 460px; margin-top: 14px; }
  .ph-madres-image { position: relative; min-height: 600px; overflow: hidden; }
  .ph-madres-image img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

  /* Occasions */
  .ph-section { padding: 80px 40px; }
  .ph-sec-head { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 56px; align-items: end; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .ph-sec-head h2 { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 52px); line-height: 1.1; color: var(--ink); }
  .ph-sec-head h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--sage-deep); }
  .ph-sec-head .ph-right { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--ink-2); max-width: 460px; }
  .ph-occasions { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--line); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .ph-occasion { background: var(--cream); padding: 48px 24px 32px; transition: background .25s; cursor: pointer; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 28px; min-height: 280px; }
  .ph-occasion:hover { background: var(--paper); }
  .ph-occasion .ph-num { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; color: var(--ink-3); font-weight: 600; }
  .ph-occasion .ph-name { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.1; color: var(--ink); }
  .ph-occasion .ph-name em { font-style: italic; color: var(--sage-deep); }
  .ph-occasion .ph-copy { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-2); margin-top: -16px; line-height: 1.5; }
  .ph-occasion .ph-arrow { margin-top: auto; font-size: 13px; color: var(--sage-deep); font-weight: 600; }
  .ph-occasion:hover .ph-arrow { color: var(--rose-deep); }

  /* Products */
  .ph-products { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 28px; }
  .ph-product { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
  .ph-product .ph-img-wrap { aspect-ratio: 4/5; background: var(--cream-2); overflow: hidden; position: relative; border-radius: 6px; }
  .ph-product .ph-img-wrap img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; transition: transform .5s; }
  .ph-product:hover .ph-img-wrap img { transform: scale(1.04); }
  .ph-product .ph-badge { position: absolute; top: 12px; left: 12px; background: var(--cream); padding: 5px 10px; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; border-radius: 4px; }
  .ph-product .ph-badge.ph-rose { background: var(--rose-deep); color: var(--cream); }
  .ph-product .ph-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; }
  .ph-product .ph-name { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-size: 21px; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.15; }
  .ph-product .ph-price { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-2); font-weight: 600; }
  .ph-product .ph-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-3); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* Photo Promise */
  .ph-photo { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; background: var(--cream-2); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .ph-photo-img { position: relative; min-height: 540px; overflow: hidden; }
  .ph-photo-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .ph-photo-text { padding: 72px 48px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; background: var(--cream); }
  .ph-photo-text h2 { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 50px); line-height: 1.1; color: var(--ink); margin-top: 16px; }
  .ph-photo-text h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--sage-deep); }
  .ph-photo-text p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ink-2); max-width: 480px; margin-top: 20px; }
  .ph-stat-row { display: flex; gap: 40px; margin-top: 36px; padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .ph-stat .ph-n { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-size: 30px; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1; }
  .ph-stat .ph-l { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: 6px; font-weight: 600; }

  /* Reviews */
  .ph-reviews { background: var(--cream); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 80px 40px; }
  .ph-reviews-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: end; margin-bottom: 40px; gap: 32px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .ph-reviews-head h2 { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 50px); line-height: 1.1; color: var(--ink); }
  .ph-reviews-head h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--sage-deep); }
  .ph-rating { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .ph-rating .ph-stars { font-size: 18px; color: #f5b454; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .ph-rating .ph-rating-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-2); font-weight: 600; }
  .ph-reviews-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
  .ph-review { background: var(--paper); padding: 28px 26px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--line); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
  .ph-review-stars { font-size: 14px; color: #f5b454; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .ph-review-text { font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.55; }
  .ph-review-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-top: auto; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .ph-review-avatar { width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--sage); color: var(--cream); display: grid; place-content: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; }
  .ph-review-name { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-2); font-weight: 600; }
  .ph-review-date { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-3); }
  .ph-reviews-cta { text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; }
  .ph-reviews-cta a { color: var(--sage-deep); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--sage-deep); padding-bottom: 2px; }
  .ph-reviews-cta a:hover { color: var(--rose-deep); border-color: var(--rose-deep); }

  /* Coverage */
  .ph-coverage { background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); padding: 80px 40px; }
  .ph-coverage-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr; gap: 56px; align-items: center; }
  .ph-coverage h2 { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 56px); line-height: 1.05; color: var(--cream); }
  .ph-coverage h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--sage-soft); }
  .ph-coverage p { color: rgba(245,239,226,.78); margin-top: 20px; max-width: 500px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .ph-zips { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 24px; }
  .ph-zips span { border: 1px solid rgba(245,239,226,.25); padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; }
  .ph-zips span.ph-active { background: var(--sage-deep); border-color: var(--sage-deep); color: var(--cream); }
  .ph-map { background: #1f1d18; aspect-ratio: 1.05/1; position: relative; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid rgba(245,239,226,.15); border-radius: 6px; }
  .ph-map iframe { width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0; display: block; filter: grayscale(.15) contrast(1.02); }
  .ph-map-caption { position: absolute; bottom: 12px; left: 12px; background: rgba(20,22,18,.9); color: var(--cream); padding: 8px 14px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; pointer-events: none; }
  .ph-map-caption a { color: var(--sage-soft); text-decoration: underline; pointer-events: auto; margin-left: 8px; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }

  /* Subs Teaser */
  .ph-subs { background: var(--paper); }
  .ph-subs-card { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; background: var(--cream); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 8px; padding: 56px 48px; text-align: center; }
  .ph-subs-card h2 { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 46px); line-height: 1.1; color: var(--ink); margin: 12px 0 18px; }
  .ph-subs-card h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--sage-deep); }
  .ph-subs-card p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--ink-2); max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 28px; }
  .ph-subs-ctas { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  /* Editorial */
  .ph-editorial { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; background: var(--cream); }
  .ph-editorial-img { min-height: 600px; overflow: hidden; }
  .ph-editorial-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .ph-editorial-text { padding: 80px 56px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
  .ph-kicker { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--sage-deep); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .ph-editorial-text h2 { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 42px); line-height: 1.2; color: var(--ink); max-width: 540px; }
  .ph-body { margin-top: 28px; max-width: 480px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ink-2); }
  .ph-body p + p { margin-top: 14px; }
  .ph-signature { font-family: var(--ph-serif); font-size: 22px; color: var(--ink); margin-top: 32px; }
  .ph-signature small { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-3); display: block; margin-top: 4px; font-weight: 600; font-family: var(--ph-sans); }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .ph-hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
    .ph-hero-text { padding: 48px 24px; }
    .ph-hero-image { min-height: 360px; }
    .ph-promise { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 28px; padding: 40px 24px; }
    .ph-section { padding: 56px 24px; }
    .ph-sec-head { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .ph-madres-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ph-madres-text { padding: 48px 24px; }
    .ph-madres-image { min-height: 360px; }
    .ph-occasions { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .ph-products { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 18px; }
    .ph-photo { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ph-photo-text { padding: 48px 24px; }
    .ph-photo-img { min-height: 320px; }
    .ph-reviews { padding: 56px 24px; }
    .ph-reviews-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ph-coverage { padding: 56px 24px; }
    .ph-coverage-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
    .ph-subs-card { padding: 40px 24px; }
    .ph-editorial { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ph-editorial-img { min-height: 360px; }
    .ph-editorial-text { padding: 48px 24px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .ph-promise { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<div class="ph">

  <section class="ph-hero">
    <div class="ph-hero-text">
      <span class="ph-eyebrow">Hand-tied. Hand-delivered. Today.</span>
      <h1>Your <em>real, local</em> Washington Heights florist.</h1>
      <p class="ph-lede">Hand-tied on Fort Washington since 2004. Walked to your door same day. We text you a photo before it leaves the shop. Hablamos español.</p>
      <div class="ph-hero-ctas">
        <a class="ph-btn ph-btn-primary" href="/collections/all">Send flowers today →</a>
        <a class="ph-btn ph-btn-ghost" href="/collections/bestsellers">Shop bestsellers</a>
      </div>
      <a class="ph-review-line" href="https://www.google.com/search?q=Primavera+Flowers+NYC+Reviews" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="stars">★★★★★</span>4.9 on Google · 200+ verified reviews</a>
      <div class="ph-hero-meta">
        <div>
          <div class="ph-label">Same-day cutoff</div>
          <div class="ph-val">2:00 PM<small>Mon to Sat</small></div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="ph-label">Delivery zone</div>
          <div class="ph-val">10033<small>10032 / 10034 / 10040</small></div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="ph-label">Bouquets from</div>
          <div class="ph-val">$59<small>Hand-tied seasonal</small></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ph-hero-image">
      <img src="{{ 'hero-roses.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Pink garden roses bouquet hand-tied at Primavera Flowers" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high">
      <div class="ph-hero-tag">
        <div class="ph-tag-label">This week</div>
        <div class="ph-tag-name">Pink Garden Roses</div>
        <div class="ph-tag-price">From $69 · same-day delivery</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ph-promise">
    <div>
      <div class="ph-num">01</div>
      <div class="ph-title">Real florist. Real shop. Real hands.</div>
      <div class="ph-desc">Not a wire service routing your order three states away. Every bouquet is built at the bench at 463 Fort Washington Ave.</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="ph-num">02</div>
      <div class="ph-title">A photo before it leaves the shop.</div>
      <div class="ph-desc">We text a quick photo of your actual bouquet, not a stock image, before it heads out the door. If it's not right, we remake it.</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="ph-num">03</div>
      <div class="ph-title">Cut this morning. Built today.</div>
      <div class="ph-desc">Our buyer is on the A train to the 28th Street market before sunrise. Stems land at the shop by 9, in your hands by 5.</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="ph-num">04</div>
      <div class="ph-title">Family-owned. Two decades. One block.</div>
      <div class="ph-desc">Bilingual, family-run on the corner of 187th since 2004. Walk in, call, or order online. By your second order we'll know your name.</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ph-madres">
    <div class="ph-madres-grid">
      <div class="ph-madres-text">
        <div class="ph-ribbon">Mother's Day · Día de las Madres · May 10</div>
        <h2>Para Mami,<br>con todo nuestro <em>cariño</em>.</h2>
        <p class="ph-es">Flores frescas entregadas hoy en todo Washington Heights. Toda la 10032, 10033, 10034 y 10040 antes de las cinco.</p>
        <p class="ph-en">Hand-tied bouquets built for the day, with a Spanish or English card in your handwriting (or ours). Order before 2 PM Saturday and we'll walk it over to Mami's apartment Sunday morning.</p>
        <div class="ph-hero-ctas" style="margin-top:28px;">
          <a class="ph-btn ph-btn-primary" href="/products/dia-de-las-madres">Shop Mother's Day →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ph-madres-image">
        <img src="{{ 'madres.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Mother's Day bouquet for delivery" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ph-section">
    <div class="ph-sec-head">
      <h2>For the <em>moments</em>, not the flowers.</h2>
      <div class="ph-right">
        <p>For the birthdays. For the apologies. For the just-because Tuesdays. Pick the moment, our designers build to the feeling. Ramos para cada momento.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ph-occasions">
      <a class="ph-occasion" href="/collections/just-because">
        <div class="ph-num">/01</div>
        <div class="ph-name">Just <em>because</em></div>
        <div class="ph-copy">For the Tuesday gesture. For the neighbor across the hall.</div>
        <div class="ph-arrow">From $48 →</div>
      </a>
      <a class="ph-occasion" href="/collections/birthday">
        <div class="ph-num">/02</div>
        <div class="ph-name"><em>Birthday</em></div>
        <div class="ph-copy">Bright stems. Soft palette. Add a candle or balloon at checkout.</div>
        <div class="ph-arrow">From $69 →</div>
      </a>
      <a class="ph-occasion" href="/collections/anniversary">
        <div class="ph-num">/03</div>
        <div class="ph-name"><em>Anniversary</em></div>
        <div class="ph-copy">Garden roses. Peonies. A proper ribbon. Same-day, same block.</div>
        <div class="ph-arrow">From $89 →</div>
      </a>
